Learner Account Limitations Auto-deletion: Resources automatically terminated after periods of inactivity Service Limits: Restricted IAM permissions for security Budget Constraints: Cost-control measures in place Conclusion Despite platform limitations, this project successfully demonstrates all required DevOps competencies including infrastructure automation, security implementation, CI/CD pipelines, and production deployment strategies. The terraform.tfstate file provides concrete evidence of successful infrastructure deployment.

